(755, 147, 'money_change', ' <h4>Money / Change</h4>\r\n                            <p>Exhibitors must make own arrangements with local banks in relation cash floats for their site.</p>'),
(756, 147, '_money_change', 'field_573c1939f8975'),
(757, 147, 'freight_contacts', ' <h4>Freight Contacts</h4>\r\n                            <p>Emerald Carrying Company  Emerald Depot 07 4982 3488</p>\r\n                            <p>NQX  Emerald Depot 07 4982 2310</p>\r\n                            <p>Followmont  07 4982 4593</p>'),
(758, 147, '_freight_contacts', 'field_573c1971f8976'),
(759, 147, 'hire_companies', '<h4>Hire Companies</h4>\r\n                            <p>Underwoods  07 4035 4513\r\n                                <br>Party Events  07 4922 4402\r\n                                <br>NJ Canvas Party Hire  07 4630 1400\r\n                                <br>Smith & Co Tent Hire  07 4982 1850\r\n                                <br>Instant Marquee Hire  07 4922 8833\r\n                                <br>Flexihire  07 4982 3488\r\n                                <br>Coates Hire  07 4982 4186\r\n                            </p>'),
(760, 147, '_hire_companies', 'field_573c1979f8977'),
(761, 147, 'never_ending', '<h4>Never-ending options at Ag-Grow Field Days</h4>\r\n                            <p>Companies often approach Administration staff with a desire to attend or have a presence at the field days but do not wish to take the tradition option of a static display. Currently there is a number of sponsorships or internal advertising within the field days, that may assist your company in gaining more direct access to your target demographic.</p>\r\n                            <p>All packages are individually tailored to produce the best results within your budget for your company. Contact Administration and allow us to assist you to shine the spotlight on your company.</p>'),
(762, 147, '_never_ending', 'field_573c1988f8978'),
(763, 147, 'launching', '<h4>Launching a new product or service</h4>\r\n                            <p>We will gladly assist you in promoting your company and/or product. Please contact the Administration Office for further assistance.</p>'),
(764, 147, '_launching', 'field_573c1996f8979'),
(765, 147, 'ag-grow_website', '<h4>Ag-Grow Website</h4>\r\n                            <p>Upon booking a site, your company will automatically be advertised via the Current Event Information page when activated in June on the Ag-Grow website (www.aggrow.com.au). To achieve the best coverage, please ensure that the Administration Office receives your current web address, contact details and product listing.</p>'),
(766, 147, '_ag-grow_website', 'field_573c19a3f897a'),
(767, 147, 'ag-grows_official_handbook', '<h4>Ag-Grows Official Handbook</h4>\r\n                            <p>The Aggrow QMIX handbook is compiled by our corporate partners, the Queensland Country Life and is inserted into approximately 25,000 newspapers throughout Queensland. It is also available to all exhibitors and visitors to Ag-Grow and QMIX. It will be used as a point of future reference for enquiring clients.</p>\r\n                            <p>If you are serious about gaining market share at Ag-Grow, advertising in the Handbook is a must. Booking and copy deadline is 1st June 2015. Pleases contact John Thompson on 07 4927 9422.</p>'),
(768, 147, '_ag-grows_official_handbook', 'field_573c19aef897b'),
(769, 147, 'radio', '<h4>Radio, TV and Press</h4>\r\n                            <p>Ag-Grow uses an extensive combination of the media to ensure that the Central Highlands and surrounding regions are aware of this annual meeting and marketing event. An intensive and thorough promotional campaign is conducted from May through to July. Should you wish to participate in this campaign to promote your company and its involvement, please contact the Administration Office who will assist you in contacting the right people for your chosen advertising media.</p>'),
(770, 147, '_radio', 'field_573c19b9f897c'),
(771, 147, 'company_flags', '<h4>Company Flags</h4>\r\n                            <p>Ag-Grow have erected a number of flag poles around the site for companys to use. Flags can be placed on your site and on the promenade during the three days. Please inform the Ag-Grow Administration Office if your company would like to take advantage of this opportunity.</p>'),
(772, 147, '_company_flags', 'field_573c19c8f897d'),
(773, 147, 'product_listing_forms', '<h4>Product Listing Forms</h4>\r\n                            <p>To correctly promote your site and business we require a current Product Listing Form to be completed. Please contact the Administration Office if you require a new form.</p>'),
(774, 147, '_product_listing_forms', 'field_573c19d5f897e'),
(775, 147, 'pa_announcements', ' <h4>PA Announcements</h4>\r\n                            <p>A public address system operates during the three days as part of your package. Ag-Grow has a professional Announcer to advertise your product or services. It is the exhibitors responsibility to ensure the Administration Office has received your companys PA announcement. During the event interviews should be conducted with the Announcer to raise your companys profile. To arrange an interview please enquire at the field days Administration Office.</p>'),
(776, 147, '_pa_announcements', 'field_573c19e4f897f'),
(777, 147, 'radio_announcements', ' <h4>Radio Announcements</h4>\r\n                            <p>Emerald 4HI are located in the Ag Pavilion and broadcast live from their site on Tuesday, Wednesday and Thursday of the field days.</p>'),
