(1340, 245, 'superior_beef_content', 'Ag-Grow not only showcases the best stud cattle producers marketing their bull for genetic versification to Northern Regions, but it has this special feature auction to establish the prices for current and future dealings between stud producer and breeder.\r\n\r\nKnown for its high clearance rate and establishment of excellent price levels the Superior Stud Bull Auction is not to be missed.\r\n\r\n<strong>For all Bull Sale enquiries, please contact:</strong>\r\n\r\nMcCaffreys Australian Livestock Marketing 07-49226311 or Ken McCaffrey 0418-792770\r\n\r\nGDL Dalby 07-46696955 or Mark Duthie 0448-016950'),
