(1444, 258, 'adam_white_content', 'Adam White runs a successful horse breaking and training business located at Highland Plains outside of Oakey Qld with his partner Jodie and family ARW Breaking and training. Adam left school at the age of 15 and headed to the gulf where he worked on stations contract mustering and breaking in horses for 10 years.'),
