(1454, 258, 'ranelle_carter_content', 'Ranelle as a junior travelled the rodeo circuit in southern NSW, earning herself a number of Barrel racing titles both in junior and open ranks and also leading her to be Rodeo queen for ABCRA.Ranelle has a Diploma in Horse Management and a Certificate III in Equine vet nursing. Also spent time with Heath Harris her mentor .Master horse trainer and movie stunt man, honing her skills as a trainer of entertainment and liberty horses.'),
