(1474, 258, 'rob_leach_content', 'Winner of the Inaugural Emerald Colt-Starting Challenge, Rob Leach has acquired a vast range of experience in the equine industry since his first full-time job for a well-known thoroughbred breaker at age 15. Rob has also had a successful competitive career both here and abroad winning and making the finals at multiple Reined Cow Horse aged events including a World Championship at the NRCHA Snaffle bit Futurity. Now based in Tamworth, Rob and his wife run their horse training business specialising in cutting, camp draft and challenge horses.'),
