(1484, 258, 'scott_keogh_content', 'Scott Keogh of SK Horsemanship operates a modern horse training facility out of Clifton, Queensland which he established in 2008 on his Spring Creek Ranch. Scott starts around 180 horses per year and offers a wide range of services from horse breaking and training to clinics and private lessons. He accepts and trains all types of horses.From a family of proven horsemen Scott is a third generation professional horseman and his motto is frustration ends where knowledge begins.'),
