(1557, 262, 'horse_sale_subheading', 'The Australian Stock Horse Sale is a regular on the Ag-Grow calendar. Featuring horses that are ideal for the hobby rider and the high end competitor, it is characterised by a vast majority of good solid stock horses ready for work immediately.'),
