(1559, 262, 'horse_sale_content', 'With cattlemen coming over from the Stud bull purchasing, they can also pick up and excellent complement for their on Farm activities. Many good genuine buying opportunities have been had at this ever popular Feature Sale.\r\n\r\n<strong>For all Horse Sale enquiries, please contact:</strong>\r\n\r\nMcCaffreys Australian Livestock Marketing 07-49226311 or Ken McCaffrey 0418-792770\r\n\r\nGDL Dalby 07-46696955 or Mark Duthie 0448-016950'),
