(2154, 357, 'aggrow_playpen_content', '<strong>Hey kids!!</strong> There is even things for you to enjoy at this years AgGrow, Come on down to AgGrows Playpen for Kids, Have loads of fun on our <strong>Jumping Castles</strong>, have your <strong>Face Painted</strong>, climb the <strong>Rock Climbing Wall</strong> and dont forget to visit <strong>Old McDonalds Farm Animals</strong> and more\r\n\r\nThis is now in a much bigger area with so much more to see and do! Mum and Dad know youre secure to have fun because the whole area is fenced off. When you come to Ag-Grow make sure you get Mum or Dad to show you where the new area is located.'),
