(3363, 530, 'adam_white_content', 'Paul Clarkson is originally from Maitland in the Hunter Valley and grew up mucking around with his two brothers around the farm with his horses and learning to ride bareback. After leaving school he followed his ambition to explore Australia, working just about any and every job that was going. After exploring Australia it was time for him to follow his passion and Paul started a breaking and training business on the Mid North Coast NSW. In conjunction with training he began to give lessons and conduct workshops and clinics. '),
