(3898, 600, 'rob_leach_content', 'Ian Francis is celebrated as a living legend, he is notabl y acknowledge d as Mr Versatil e. This is due\r\nto his comprehensive list of achievement s across a multitude of discipline s .\r\nHis Stockhorse Challenge successes include, twice winning the C loncurry Stockmans Challenge and\r\nthe Widgee Stock Horse futurity with 2,3 and 4 year old Champions.\r\nIan has also triumphed in the sport of Working Cowhorse, acquiring numerous titles including\r\nMoonbi Cowhorse Futurity Champions twice and Reserve Champions twice, six times Queensland\r\nCowhorse Futurity Champion, and five times AHQA Working Cowhorse of the Year.'),
