(13, 1, '2016-05-17 10:19:22', '2016-05-17 10:19:22', '<img class="size-medium wp-image-339 alignleft" src="http://aggrow.stagingdevsite.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/major-sponsors-img-300x57.png" alt="major-sponsors-img" width="300" height="57" />Westpac Agribusiness is proud to once again be the major sponsor of Ag-Grow 2015. This great event allows us to continue our support for agribusiness and the local community.\r\nIn fact, 2017 will mark our 200th year backing Australias farmers and agricultural businesses. In that time, weve forged strong partnerships with customers, communities and industry in rural Australia.\r\nWere committed to sharing the journey with you into the future. And as we enter our third century, we remain focused on helping Australia prosper and grow.\r\nCertainly, the future is bright for Australian agriculture, thanks to the resilient farmers and agricultural businesses like you, who are dedicated to innovating and improving the industry. By embracing cutting-edge practices and technologies, you help cement our industrys top position on the world stage and secure Australias farming future.\r\nWe see that passion every day in Emerald and across Central Queensland. And its why we continue to support Ag-Grow  because we believe in local farmers and agribusiness and are here to help you make the most of every opportunity.', 'Major Sponsors', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'major-sponsors', '', '', '2016-06-02 07:10:51', '2016-06-02 07:10:51', '', 0, 'http://aggrow.stagingdevsite.com/dev/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
