(19, 1, '2016-05-17 10:28:05', '2016-05-17 10:28:05', 'We are more than just a farm show  we are an agribusiness field day, a window into what we believe is one of the most innovative, forward thinking agricultural economies in the world. Our role is to connect business to business, business to consumer, exporter with new markets and town with country. As we enter our 27th year, we are working harder than ever to connect people and organisations, to create opportunities, to facilitate the open exchange of ideas and to showcase the very best Australian agriculture has to offer.\r\n\r\nThe three days of the Ag-Grow field days are designed not only to showcase to a wide audience, but the latest in products, services, and technology that our exhibitors have to offer and also to build long lasting friendships, renew existing relationships and widen business networking opportunities in a relaxed, in the field environment.\r\n\r\nThe essence of Ag-Grow Field Days is never more pertinent than in a challenging economic market such as we are experiencing at the moment with the downturn in the mining industry in our region, making it interesting and challenging times.\r\n\r\nIt is all the more reason to celebrate the diversity of products and industries in our Central Highlands and Central West area.\r\n\r\nEvery year we are investing in the Ag-Grow grounds to make everyones experience the best we can possibly offer and this year is no exception.\r\n\r\nI would like to welcome our new exhibitors for 2016 and hopeyou have a very successful Ag-Grow, remembering that business is not confined only to the 3 days of the field days but with good business can lead to long and prosperous relationships. A philosophy Ag-Grow itself strives to adhere to and this is apparent with the return of our loyal exhibitors which we would also like to welcome back to Ag-Grow and Emerald.\r\n\r\nI would like to say thank you to all of our Sponsors, existing exhibitors and new exhibitors for all your continued support year after year\r\n\r\n<strong>Donna Reeves</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Manager</strong>', 'Why Exhibit At Ag-grow', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'why-exhibit-at-ag-grow', '', '', '2016-06-15 09:33:42', '2016-06-15 09:33:42', '', 0, 'http://aggrow.stagingdevsite.com/dev/?page_id=19', 0, 'page', '', 0),
