(249, 1, '2016-05-19 07:49:34', '2016-05-19 07:49:34', '<strong>CENTRAL HIGHLANDS COLT STARTING CHALLENGE</strong>\r\n\r\nFeaturing at Ag-Grow 3 years ago, this remarkable event demonstrates horse whispering at its best. Three unridden colts are matched with three contestants who progressively encourage trust and bonding from the animal until it can finally be ridden and perform tasks traditionally reserved for a much longer break in period.\r\n\r\nIn two days these horses go from wild to mild in a demonstration that is nothing short of remarkable. This is a great attraction that keeps building in popularity as the years go by.\r\n\r\nEvents over 2 Days:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>3 Competitors</li>\r\n 	<li>3 Horseman &amp; Women</li>\r\n 	<li>3 Different Techniques</li>\r\n 	<li>3 Round Pens</li>\r\n 	<li>6 Untouched Colts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThree top Australian Horseman who all have National &amp; International Horse Training experience.Three horses that have never been ridden, come along and experience the excitement', 'Colt Challange', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '37-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-19 07:49:34', '2016-05-19 07:49:34', '', 37, 'http://aggrow.stagingdevsite.com/dev/37-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
